The questrian Center operates an affordable, extensive year-round program in English and Western riding, beginning through advanced levels. Offers successive, week-long summer camps for kids that include riding and swimming. Specialized classes are offered in Eventing, Hunter/Jumper, Dressage, Western, and team competition. Tours and birthday party trail rides are available. Call to request a mini-catalog of Equestrian Center activities.

*the website was down at the time of this writing, 11-Dec.
